Controversial rapper Erigga has attempted to explain what is responsible for most taxi engines getting damaged in Nigeria. He made this known following response from a Twitter user simply identified as bee Graffiti. Paper boi posed a question to his fans seeking to know how coitus can damage a car engine. He tweeted: “How car s3x take dey spoil engine?”   Lateef Adedimeji as Tinubu in movie: I’m prepared for…     Why I feel like giving up, by Mr Macaroni     Pretty Mike attends party with ladies dressed as animals   He got several responses however bee Graffiti’s caught his attention and the “Problem No Dey Finish” singer decided to re-share it. The tweet reads: “Knack girls for the car during my hustle with Uber and Taxify. I knack one for the boot of my matrix, said she never enjoyed s3x like this. “Dashed me 20k, told her friend, come knack her, dashed me 20k connected me with offline clients everywhere for Abuja, bought my own car within 4 months.”